{"tid":2342863,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「月經廢文」學好英文真係好似打開新世界咁","createTime":"2020-12-27T12:47:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T14:01:57.000Z","uid":182333,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1e0f268e0047bef50ea47824adf1049b18742201","tid":2342863,"uid":182333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T12:47:56.000Z","msg":"細個個時唔覺，仲以為網上咁發達<br />\n只要識中文 就會好多野都可以學到 所以一直都冇認真學英文 dse都只係負負碌碌pass左就算<br />\n冇話打算特別進修<br />\n但大大下先發現好多資料華文世界都冇/冇英文文獻咁齊<br />\n<br />\n好彩地 因為某d興趣令我焗住要我睇外國d youtube channel<br />\n咁先可以令我pick up返d英文<br />\n而到上個月買左人生第一本書英文(唔係教科書)黎咪下<br />\n發現原來曾經dse 英文得2既人都可以睇曬 個刻真係差d喊出黎<br />\n<br />\n如果有讀緊中學既連登仔 千祈唔好當英文只係一門科目咁讀 令佢黎應付考試就算<br />\n學好佢 佢真係可以為你打通世界既大門咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"984aee5c6b65375f64a1cfbfda0443d297bb3d6f","tid":2342863,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T12:55:42.000Z","msg":"點為止學好商用英文書寫✍️"},{"pid":"65eb5671e0ec1e7247027dc5d8382b5402fd18b9","tid":2342863,"uid":182333,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"984aee5c6b65375f64a1cfbfda0443d297bb3d6f","tid":2342863,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T12:55:42.000Z","msg":"點為止學好商用英文書寫✍️"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T12:57:24.000Z","msg":"ching 我答左你 你都唔好信我喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68a7d32de92ae342ee69b3abb4c4553cebc8ccca","tid":2342863,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T13:04:29.000Z","msg":"樓主點樣Pick up英文？<br />\n我第一屆DSE英文拎u<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已經好多年冇睇過英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\